what is Express ?

- Node JS Web Framework.
- opensource Framework developed and maintained by node JS Foundation
- Express is a minimal and flixible, fast node JS web framework that provides set of featurs for web developement.
- impliment routing, HTTP Server,Protocol, Process, URL - express

